    <briefdescription>
<para>Marker component attached to entities whose health has been depleted. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Systems can query for <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1lifecycle_1_1components_1_1DeadTagComponent" kindref="compound">DeadTagComponent</ref> to apply death-related logic (e.g. scoring, VFX, cleanup) without re-checking health values. Move-only; copying is not permitted. </para>
